    "body": "Hi @yashbhavsar007 I unfortunately think that we will not get to this feature given it is not as necessary as one may think. Validator doppelganger detection is, for the most part, the best way to prevent slashings even if you lose your slashing protection history and have to restart your validator. These approaches have been working fine for most users and there are other features we would like to prioritize in Prysm",
